===Transitive verb===
{{en-infl-reg-consonant|boil||}}

# To heat (a liquid) to the point where it begins to turn into a gas.
#:'''''Boil''' some water in a pan.''
# To [[cook]] in boiling water.
#:'''''Boil''' the eggs for two minutes.''

